OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe lawyer representing the families
OL,8,Fin the Corby toxic waste scandal is
OL,9,Fjoining MPs in Corby and Kettering in
OL,10,Ftheir calls for a public inquiry into
OL,11,Fwhat happened.
OL,13,FThe scandal involved a series of birth
OL,14,Fdefects in children born to mothers
OL,15,Fliving near the former steelworks in
OL,16,FCorby.
OL,18,FFollowing the closure of the
OL,19,Fsteelworks in the 1980s, the area was
OL,20,Fredeveloped and millions of tonnes of
OL,21,Ftoxic waste were moved.
