OL,7,FHe along with Lee Barron MP and Rosie
OL,8,FWrighting MP have sent a letter to
OL,9,FNorth Northamptonshire council
OL,10,Fdemanding they reveal where they got
OL,11,Frid of the waste.
OL,13,F'Tell us where this stuff is buried'
OL,15,FDes said: "We think the majority of
OL,16,Fthe waste was put into landfill, the
OL,17,Fsuggestion being made at the moment is
OL,18,Fthey didn't know to bury the waste
OL,19,Fproperly.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
