OL,3,CLawyer who represented families in
OL,4,Ctoxic waste scandal calls for public
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"We are going to ask the council
OL,8,Fagainst the background of the 2009
OL,9,Fjudgement to tell us exactly where
OL,10,Fthis stuff is buried and if they don't
OL,11,Fknow, why they don't know.
OL,13,F"There should be a public inquiry into
OL,14,FCorby because that's something we
OL,15,Fbelieved should be addressed by
OL,16,Fgovernment, because it doesn't stand
OL,17,Fup to scrutiny that they know stuff
OL,18,Fwas moved and moved badly.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
