OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"The way to sort this out is for the
OL,8,Fcouncil to say this is how it's
OL,9,Fburied, this is where it's buried,
OL,10,Fthis is testing we have done to show
OL,11,Fthat there is nothing wrong here but
OL,12,Fthis is not what they are doing."
OL,14,FWhat did the high court case find?
OL,16,FThe case which involved 18 families,
OL,17,Fconclusively showed that the birth
OL,18,Fdefects seen in children and babies
OL,19,Fliving in the town was because of
OL,20,Fairborne waste.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
