OL,7,FIt also found that Corby Borough
OL,8,FCouncil did not dispose of the waste
OL,9,Fcorrectly and that they were negligent
OL,10,Fin managing it.
OL,12,FIt also established that the material
OL,13,Fhad been in the ground and that the
OL,14,Fwaste could cause embryonic birth
OL,15,Fdefects.
OL,17,FToxic Town
