OL,7,FThe scandal has been brought more into
OL,8,Fpublic attention through the Netflix
OL,9,Fshow Toxic Town which tells the
OL,10,Fstories of a group of mothers who
OL,11,Fjoined together to fight for justice.
OL,13,FThe drama centres around three of the
OL,14,Fmothers at the centre of the scandal
OL,15,Fwho fought for justice after their
OL,16,Fchildren were born with birth defects.
OL,18,FMost of the children were born with
OL,19,Fmissing fingers or toes - a phenomenon
OL,20,Freferred to at the time as "Corby
OL,21,FHand" - and some of the babies died.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
