OL,7,FDes said: "Around 30 or 40 families
OL,8,Fhave come to us since Toxic Town with
OL,9,Fconcerns about birth defects such as
OL,10,Fleukaemia."
OL,12,FCouncil response
OL,14,FWe've contacted North Northamptonshire
OL,15,FCouncil, which took over functions
OL,16,Ffrom Corby Borough Council, and await
OL,17,Fa response.
